## Design Tokens Usage

Always use InsureCo design tokens тАФ never hardcode colors or spacing values.

### Colors
- `--interactive-primary` тАФ Brand red for buttons and accents
- `--background-primary` тАФ Main background
- `--background-secondary` тАФ Alternate section backgrounds
- `--text-primary` тАФ Main text color
- `--text-secondary` тАФ Supporting text color
- `--text-on-color` тАФ White text on colored backgrounds
- `--color-success` тАФ Checkmark icons

### Spacing
- `--spacing-03` through `--spacing-13` тАФ Component spacing
- `--section-spacing` тАФ Between major sections

### Typography
- `--heading-h1-size` through `--heading-h4-size`
- `--body-lg-size`, `--body-md-size`, `--body-sm-size`

### Layout
- Carbon Grid system (16 columns)
- Responsive breakpoints: `sm` (< 672px), `md` (672тАУ1056px), `lg` (> 1056px)

### Motion
- `--motion-hover` тАФ Button and tile hover transitions

