## Responsive Design

### Mobile (< 672px)
- Hero heading size reduced; CTA buttons stack vertically
- `SplitHero` reflows to single column
- Reduced padding and minimum heights

### Tablet (672pxтАУ1056px)
- Two-column layouts for some sections
- Adjusted image placeholder sizes

### Desktop (> 1056px)
- Full multi-column layouts; larger hero section

